WEBVTT

00:00:03.100 --> 00:00:07.397
THIS IS TAPE NUMBER TWO. A INTERVIEW WITH ESTHER LEWITAN.

00:00:09.192 --> 00:00:10.235
Ester

00:00:10.235 --> 00:00:12.324
kh'vil tsurikgeyn a bisele.

00:00:12.938 --> 00:00:16.782
kh'vil dir fregn, ven du bist arayngelofn in vald

00:00:16.782 --> 00:00:18.618
bistu geven aleynt?

00:00:19.047 --> 00:00:21.825
ver, ver iz geven mit dir?

00:00:20.190 --> 00:00:22.280
NO, nokh mentshn geven.

00:00:22.557 --> 00:00:24.981
du gedenkst ver du bist geven mi-?

00:00:24.733 --> 00:00:29.637
di, di nemen gedenk ikh nit vayl s'iz geven umbakante mentshn.

00:00:29.712 --> 00:00:33.688
nor az zey flegn zen az mayn man ge- brengt mir epes

00:00:33.812 --> 00:00:35.949
flegn zey zayn JEALOUS,

00:00:36.023 --> 00:00:38.028
flegn zey zogn, "zest,

00:00:38.028 --> 00:00:41.653
ir git er, un undz git er gornisht nit".

00:00:41.676 --> 00:00:45.095
zey hobn nit farshtanen az epes hot er a gefil

00:00:45.523 --> 00:00:50.242
az, az er git mir ontsuton, un er git mir vos tsu esn.

00:00:50.282 --> 00:00:54.447
BUT frier ven du host ge- ge- bakvent dikh mit dayn man,

00:00:54.447 --> 00:00:59.493
du bist aley- du bist geven aleynt ven du bist gelofn in vald, nisht mit keyne

00:00:59.493 --> 00:01:01.380
kuzine oder...?

00:01:00.220 --> 00:01:02.628
NO, un ikh bin gezes-

00:01:02.905 --> 00:01:06.561
ge- gezesn in vald lebn a boym un geveynt.

00:01:06.820 --> 00:01:12.366
(biz) vanet a mentsh iz gekumen un er hot mir gezogt, "Ester, vos vilstu?

00:01:12.591 --> 00:01:16.652
mir'n blaybn lebn. du'st zen, mir'n blaybn lebn".

00:01:16.776 --> 00:01:24.846
hot er mir u- gemakht dem lebn ziser, gek- hob ikh geklert az efsher take iz er gerekht.

00:01:25.163 --> 00:01:27.708
efsher vel ikh take blaybn lebn.

00:01:27.677 --> 00:01:30.286
ver iz dos geven vos hot geredt tsu dir?

00:01:31.744 --> 00:01:35.170
 ven iz dos geven?

00:01:34.174 --> 00:01:36.817
ver iz ge- dos geven vos hot gezogt,

00:01:36.823 --> 00:01:38.184
vest lebn?

00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:38.170
o, d-

00:01:38.170 --> 00:01:42.640
a por yidn, a por yidn hobn zikh nor (gebrakht tsu undz) in vald.

00:01:43.472 --> 00:01:48.101
un dernokh, yetst hostu mir oykhet gezogt az du host gegat a fraynt

00:01:48.101 --> 00:01:49.898
vos dayn man hot gehelft.

00:01:49.898 --> 00:01:51.358
zey zenen geven krank.

00:01:51.350 --> 00:01:52.510
ye

00:01:51.358 --> 00:01:54.704
kenstu gedenken ver, di nomen un ver zey...?

00:01:54.623 --> 00:01:59.717
ye, ye, zayn nomen iz geven Yoysef, un zi iz geven Roze.

00:02:00.330 --> 00:02:02.399
un zey hobn gehat a yingele.

00:02:03.283 --> 00:02:06.343
gedenk nit vi m'hot im gerufn.

00:02:04.954 --> 00:02:06.348
un zey lebn?

00:02:06.343 --> 00:02:07.128
ye.

00:02:07.128 --> 00:02:08.739
ye, zey lebn.

00:02:08.739 --> 00:02:12.204
un der zun iz, der yingl iz gevorn a dokter

00:02:12.548 --> 00:02:14.769
un zaynen geven in ISRAEL.

00:02:15.028 --> 00:02:17.435
yetst veys ikh nit vu zey zaynen.

00:02:19.213 --> 00:02:25.467
SO ven du bist, yetst kumst, yetst hostu oysgefunen, az, az di krig iz endikt

00:02:26.773 --> 00:02:29.990
un vos iz geven mit, far dir d-

00:02:30.958 --> 00:02:34.175
ge- gefregt bay alemen

00:02:35.515 --> 00:02:38.783
(tsu hot men zey) gezen emetser fun mayn FAMILY.

00:02:38.907 --> 00:02:41.196
keynem hobn zey nit gezen.

00:02:41.438 --> 00:02:43.659
ven zey hobn nokh gelebt

00:02:43.783 --> 00:02:44.941
in vald

00:02:45.201 --> 00:02:48.890
hob ikh gefregt bay zey. zey hobn keynem nit gezen.

00:02:48.947 --> 00:02:50.704
ale tseharget.

00:02:50.922 --> 00:02:55.894
vi hos- vi bistu geganen ven du bist aroysgekumen fun vald?

00:02:56.068 --> 00:02:59.099
gegangen tsurik tsu meyn heym.

00:02:59.275 --> 00:03:01.159
gornit gefunen.

00:03:01.266 --> 00:03:03.015
nor di erd.

00:03:03.477 --> 00:03:07.706
bin ikh avek tsu di goyim betn vos ontsuton

00:03:07.932 --> 00:03:09.726
un vos tsu esn.

00:03:09.726 --> 00:03:15.502
(vos) andere hobn mir gegebn. zey hobn gezogt, "LEYBOVA DOTSHKA, NUZHNO DAVAT'".

00:03:15.981 --> 00:03:18.399
hobn zey mir gegebn vos tsu esn

00:03:18.399 --> 00:03:19.859
nokh der milkhome.

00:03:19.727 --> 00:03:21.796
du bist geb- -ven aleynt?

00:03:21.786 --> 00:03:26.657
bin aleyn, hot, un mayn man iz geven shoyn mit mir, ye.

00:03:25.768 --> 00:03:26.487
ye.

00:03:26.713 --> 00:03:31.381
vos er hot gekent derkazhen(en) hot er geken- gekont.

00:03:31.557 --> 00:03:34.268
ober di goyim hobn gegebn

00:03:34.341 --> 00:03:35.904
vos ontsuton.

00:03:36.163 --> 00:03:37.625
vos tsu esn.

00:03:38.290 --> 00:03:43.751
un zey hobn gezogt, "(vu) veln mir zikh onnemen ah di yidn tsu kormenen".

00:03:43.943 --> 00:03:45.827
zog ikh vi- vi-

00:03:45.850 --> 00:03:51.682
vifl vet ir undz darfn kormenen? yeder eyner vos ken arbetn vet geyn arbetn.

00:03:53.207 --> 00:03:54.854
un azoy iz geven.

00:03:55.333 --> 00:03:59.152
yeder eyner iz avek zukhn vi tsu makhn a lebn

00:03:59.152 --> 00:04:00.964
un vi tsu krign

00:04:01.138 --> 00:04:04.603
vos tsu esn un a da- a dakh ibern kop.

00:04:04.598 --> 00:04:11.240
du'st geshteyt in dayn, in, in di, in dayn shtot, oder bist geganen in an andersh veg?

00:04:10.660 --> 00:04:14.750
ye, un mayn shtot iz oykh geblibn mentshn, ye.

00:04:14.824 --> 00:04:16.455
un vu bistu geven?

00:04:16.613 --> 00:04:19.611
du host geshteyt in dayn shtub OR iz avekgeforn?

00:04:19.700 --> 00:04:23.508
neyn, mayn shtub iz nit geven. geven opgebrent.

00:04:24.848 --> 00:04:27.036
mayn shtub iz nit geven.

00:04:27.598 --> 00:04:31.068
ikh bin geven m- tsuzamen mit (yidn)

00:04:31.615 --> 00:04:35.389
ikh (bin) shoyn nit gekent zayn in vald, hob ikh gezukht

00:04:35.580 --> 00:04:40.737
mit yidn tsu zayn, un ikh hob gehat mayn man, iz zaynen mir geven tsuzamen.

00:04:41.385 --> 00:04:43.640
un nakher zaynen mir

00:04:44.271 --> 00:04:47.184
zaynen mir geven in

00:04:48.338 --> 00:04:50.559
gehat ot di BUSINESS.

00:04:54.075 --> 00:05:00.026
emetser hot dir gehelf- geholfn ven du bist geganen tsu dayn shtot nokhn vald?

00:05:01.568 --> 00:05:04.177
emetser hot dir, hot geholfn?

00:05:03.990 --> 00:05:04.920
ye, ye.

00:05:04.622 --> 00:05:06.388
ver hot dir geholfn?

00:05:06.428 --> 00:05:08.076
a poyer.

00:05:08.082 --> 00:05:11.687
poyerim un mayn man. ikh hob dokh gehat mayn man.

00:05:11.760 --> 00:05:15.432
un er iz dokh geven a partizaner, hot er gekent krign

00:05:15.658 --> 00:05:18.132
vos tsu esn, vos ontsuton.

00:05:21.700 --> 00:05:26.318
du bist geshtanen in dayn shtot, ober du bist avekgeforn?

00:05:26.057 --> 00:05:27.837
ye, in mayn shtot.

00:05:27.606 --> 00:05:29.321
nisht avekgeforn?

00:05:28.947 --> 00:05:32.000
neyn, neyn, nit avekgeforn.

00:05:32.161 --> 00:05:36.290
ikh hob geklert efsher vet nokh emetser kumen, a bruder, a UNK

00:05:36.094 --> 00:05:37.303
vi lang?

00:05:37.220 --> 00:05:40.120
a shviger, un keyner iz nit gekumen.

00:05:40.701 --> 00:05:44.542
un m'hot gezogt az me hot zey alemen tsebrent un tsehakt.

00:05:47.485 --> 00:05:51.984
brenen un hargenen (volt nokh nit oysmakhn) shtiker geshnitn.

00:05:52.210 --> 00:05:54.178
a BOY a yunger

00:05:54.589 --> 00:05:55.809
hot ge-

00:05:55.809 --> 00:05:58.779
hot avekgeleygt a ferd, iz gelegn

00:05:58.779 --> 00:06:00.551
fun etlekhe teg.

00:06:00.551 --> 00:06:05.614
di flign hobn shoyn im gegesn. khayes farsheydene oyf im geven,

00:06:05.614 --> 00:06:08.168
un er hot geshnitn mit a meserl

00:06:08.173 --> 00:06:13.752
a shtikele fun, fun ale zaytn fun dem ferd un hot gegesn.

00:06:13.827 --> 00:06:17.325
hobn mir im gezogt, "Yisroelke, vi tustu dos?"

00:06:17.325 --> 00:06:21.330
zogt er, "ikh khalesh tsu esn. ikh hob nit vos."

00:06:21.657 --> 00:06:25.093
hob ikh im, hobn mir im gegebn vos mir hobn gehat

00:06:25.605 --> 00:06:29.126
un er hot ge- geSTOPt mitn ferd

00:06:29.976 --> 00:06:32.552
un hot geshnitn shtiklekh ferd.

00:06:36.658 --> 00:06:38.727
s'iz gornit tsu (dernemen).

00:06:39.004 --> 00:06:44.398
Ester, vi lang hostu geshteyn in dayn shtot? vos iz di nomen fun dayn shtot?

00:06:44.367 --> 00:06:45.599
gornit.

00:06:45.282 --> 00:06:47.874
un vi lang hostu dortn geshtanen?

00:06:49.062 --> 00:06:52.718
ikh veys aleyn nit, geven etlekhe yor.

00:06:53.989 --> 00:06:56.871
etlekhe yor (fun) vanet mir hobn zikh ayngeordnt.

00:06:56.841 --> 00:06:58.539
du'st gegat kinder?

00:06:58.579 --> 00:06:59.433
ye.

00:07:00.368 --> 00:07:02.809
kh'hob gehat fir tekhter.

00:07:02.950 --> 00:07:07.402
AND ver, ven, eyn tokhter iz geborn dortn, ober

00:07:07.402 --> 00:07:10.065
vu iz di tokhter geborn, di ershte tokhter?

00:07:10.341 --> 00:07:12.967
di eltere tokhter iz geborn

00:07:13.159 --> 00:07:16.460
mir dukht az take in ir eygener shtetl.

00:07:17.310 --> 00:07:19.565
gornit, (ikh gedenk) gornit.

00:07:19.993 --> 00:07:22.332
gedenk nit (vu zey) zaynen geborn.

00:07:25.393 --> 00:07:29.909
ober m'iz umgeforn. m'iz nit gezesn oyf eyn plats.

00:07:34.725 --> 00:07:37.014
du gedenkst vu du bist geforn?

00:07:41.543 --> 00:07:42.988
fargesn oykh.

00:07:43.804 --> 00:07:44.878
fargesn.

00:07:45.357 --> 00:07:46.653
SO

00:07:46.653 --> 00:07:49.589
AND dernokh, vi azoy

00:07:49.589 --> 00:07:54.412
bistu gekumen, du bist f- gef- avekgeforn fun Rusland, yo?

00:07:55.110 --> 00:07:56.761
ye, ye.

00:07:56.761 --> 00:07:57.416
ye.

00:07:57.743 --> 00:08:00.673
ye, mir zaynen avekgeforn fun Rusland

00:08:00.763 --> 00:08:03.406
un hobn gelebt in Minsk

00:08:04.257 --> 00:08:06.596
un nakher zaynen mir

00:08:06.990 --> 00:08:10.089
gelebt in andere shtet.

00:08:10.737 --> 00:08:12.739
in Lodzh hobn mir gelebt,

00:08:15.462 --> 00:08:18.915
in Lodzh zaynen mir geven ayngeordnt dort a bisl.

00:08:18.921 --> 00:08:21.412
vi lang hostu gelebt in Lodzh?

00:08:21.925 --> 00:08:24.939
in Lodzh hobn mir gemuzt, gemuzt lebn a

00:08:25.266 --> 00:08:26.604
a dray yor

00:08:26.604 --> 00:08:27.909
tsu fir yor.

00:08:28.202 --> 00:08:30.170
du host gegat mer kinder

00:08:31.020 --> 00:08:35.266
dernokh ershte tokhter? vos iz di nomen fun di ershte tokhter?

00:08:34.630 --> 00:08:37.260
ARLENE. nokh mayn muter, ye.

00:08:35.559 --> 00:08:36.430
AND

00:08:36.825 --> 00:08:39.418
AND zi iz geboyrn in velkhe shtot?

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:44.890
I'M GONNA TELL THE TRUTH, ikh gedenk nit. zey gedenken, di kinder.

00:08:44.925 --> 00:08:50.201
AND dernokh ve- vifl y- vifl yor biz di nekste tokhter iz geboyrn?

00:08:45.270 --> 00:08:47.350
UNK

00:08:52.148 --> 00:08:55.618
zey zaynen ale in dray yor gerukt.

00:08:56.350 --> 00:08:58.740
di eltere iz

00:08:59.067 --> 00:09:00.860
geven

00:09:00.860 --> 00:09:03.987
finf, hob ikh gehat an ander tokhter

00:09:05.040 --> 00:09:09.539
un er hot ge- mayn man gebenkt, "far vos hob ikh nit keyn zin?"

00:09:09.563 --> 00:09:13.387
iz itster do in Amerike, iz itster oyfn zun

00:09:13.596 --> 00:09:16.967
zogt er, "itster vel ikh hobn a zun".

00:09:16.967 --> 00:09:19.783
zog ikh, "NO, mayn tayerer. s'iz (nokh) tsu shpet."

00:09:20.582 --> 00:09:22.786
oybe er hot gedarft frier.

00:09:24.649 --> 00:09:29.250
vu zenen dayn tokhter geboyrn? du gedenkst vu, velkhe shtot?

00:09:29.391 --> 00:09:30.476
gedenk nit.

00:09:30.403 --> 00:09:32.155
geven in, in

00:09:32.155 --> 00:09:36.067
Poyland, DEUTSCHLAND, Amerike? du gedenkst nisht?

00:09:34.810 --> 00:09:36.720
(gornit).

00:09:36.720 --> 00:09:40.455
in (mir dukht zikh) shoyn in Amerike.

00:09:42.520 --> 00:09:44.252
di meydlekh veysn.

00:09:44.393 --> 00:09:47.070
bay zey iz alts farshribn oyf CARDS

00:09:47.700 --> 00:09:50.917
un oyf BIRTHDAY CARDS, un zey veysn

00:09:51.261 --> 00:09:53.360
genoy ikh veys shoyn nit.

00:09:53.438 --> 00:09:55.170
mayn kop UNK shoyn

00:09:55.665 --> 00:09:58.612
nit fun altkeyt nor fun tsores.

00:09:59.125 --> 00:10:05.649
hostu oysgefunen ah fun dayn familye ven du bist geven in

00:10:06.398 --> 00:10:09.753
DEUTSCHLAND ober in Lodzh ober in

00:10:09.753 --> 00:10:10.914
ven du bist

00:10:11.038 --> 00:10:12.348
geganen a-

00:10:13.401 --> 00:10:18.221
in Daytshland iz mayner a bruder geven, geharget gevorn

00:10:18.480 --> 00:10:19.807
mit a vayb

00:10:20.860 --> 00:10:25.427
un, (ikh vel) zogn dir dem emes, ikh shem zikh gor tsu zogn

00:10:25.602 --> 00:10:28.363
az ikh hob a plimenitse in Berlin

00:10:29.837 --> 00:10:32.109
zi fi- firt

00:10:32.149 --> 00:10:34.606
a fayne heym un iz raykh

00:10:34.984 --> 00:10:39.045
ober di FAMILY iz oysgeharget gevorn.

00:10:40.502 --> 00:10:41.896
vos iz di nomen?

00:10:42.409 --> 00:10:44.445
UNK ikh

00:10:44.586 --> 00:10:48.225
mayn man iz in kaas oyf ir, vayl vos zi tut UNK, geshikt

00:10:48.332 --> 00:10:50.334
yetst a shone-toyve

00:10:51.066 --> 00:10:52.612
UNK

00:10:52.770 --> 00:10:57.337
zogt er, "shtel zikh for. eyn plimenitse iz geblibn

00:10:57.883 --> 00:11:00.239
un zi lebt, a dank got.

00:11:00.837 --> 00:11:03.362
halt zi keyn shone-toyve un

00:11:03.570 --> 00:11:06.495
halt zi, zi iz, zi, shraybn a briv.

00:11:06.495 --> 00:11:11.850
zi flegt grade shraybn az er hot gelebt. yetst iz er geshtorbn, der man.

00:11:11.873 --> 00:11:13.301
shraybt zi nit.

00:11:13.543 --> 00:11:17.671
az er hot gelebt flegt er shraybn un rufn oyfn TELEPHONE.

00:11:17.998 --> 00:11:20.742
ale mol un fregn vos me makht

00:11:21.508 --> 00:11:24.101
un shikn di kinder prezenter.

00:11:24.462 --> 00:11:26.163
ober yetst

00:11:26.163 --> 00:11:28.876
hot zi opgehakt, vil mayn man oykh nit

00:11:29.372 --> 00:11:32.251
visn. ikh zog, "lomir a CALL ton

00:11:32.646 --> 00:11:34.834
un mir veln visn vos s'hert zikh".

00:11:35.042 --> 00:11:38.951
zogt er, "NO, zi iz aza khazer. zi iz azoy raykh

00:11:39.227 --> 00:11:43.507
un zi shikt keyn PENNY, un s- gornisht.

00:11:43.665 --> 00:11:46.089
vil ikh (zikh nit) dervisn fun ir".

00:11:46.433 --> 00:11:48.131
er iz gerekht oykh.

00:11:48.643 --> 00:11:49.734
emes?

00:11:50.618 --> 00:11:52.485
nit azoy darf zayn.

00:11:52.727 --> 00:11:56.804
nokh aza fintsterer milkhome vos ikh hob al-

00:11:57.064 --> 00:11:58.998
alemen farlorn.

00:12:00.743 --> 00:12:01.800
Ester,

00:12:02.228 --> 00:12:04.399
du gedenkst efsher

00:12:04.607 --> 00:12:09.916
frier, ven du bist ge- du bist geforn dernokh tsu Amerike?

00:12:10.227 --> 00:12:11.017
ye.

00:12:10.969 --> 00:12:15.750
frier fun du bist geforn tsu Amerike, vi azoy iz oysgekumen

00:12:15.699 --> 00:12:17.125
(dos iz) di brider

00:12:15.750 --> 00:12:17.409
az du kenst forn?

00:12:17.125 --> 00:12:20.599
mayn man's brider hobn geshikt PAPERS.

00:12:21.465 --> 00:12:25.171
mayn man's, mayn man hot oykh gehat tsvey brider.

00:12:25.819 --> 00:12:29.802
hot, hobn zey geshikt PAPERS oyf tsu kumen in Amerike.

00:12:31.152 --> 00:12:35.904
AND, AND ven frier fun forn tsu Amerike, vu hostu gelebt?

00:12:36.518 --> 00:12:39.499
in velkhe shtot, OR efsher in a (CAMP)?

00:12:39.070 --> 00:12:42.334
s'iz geven dokh vos me hot gegebn hilf,

00:12:42.846 --> 00:12:46.181
geven vos m'hot gegebn hilf oyf tsum lebn

00:12:46.238 --> 00:12:47.801
un a dire

00:12:47.807 --> 00:12:48.993
(iz oykh) geven.

00:12:48.993 --> 00:12:51.210
Amerike iz a gute land.

00:12:51.807 --> 00:12:54.163
zi hot undz avekgeshtelt oyf di fis.

00:12:55.131 --> 00:12:58.939
host gegat papirn ven du bist aroysgekumen fun vald?

00:12:59.248 --> 00:13:00.122
ye.

00:13:00.075 --> 00:13:01.182
papirn?

00:13:00.122 --> 00:13:04.164
ah, papirn fun vald hob ikh nit gehat gornisht.

00:13:04.007 --> 00:13:06.937
vi azoy hostu gekrign papirn?

00:13:07.365 --> 00:13:10.278
in Daytshland hot, zikh farshribn

00:13:10.825 --> 00:13:13.603
ober gekrogn hobn mir keyn zakh nit.

00:13:14.537 --> 00:13:19.580
un er iz gegangen arbetn, un ikh bin gegangen arbetn, un m'hot gelebt.

00:13:19.380 --> 00:13:21.584
vos KIND arbet hostu gemakht?

00:13:21.574 --> 00:13:23.070
ikh hob hitlekh

00:13:23.278 --> 00:13:26.596
menske hitlekh. dos iz geven di arbet.

